com.oracle.sfp.scripting.api

Interface INfrConfigAPI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IScriptingObject

    public interface INfrConfigAPI
extends IScriptingObject
    Interface of the scripting API objects meant to be passed as the "nfrConfig" binding to NFR config scripts so that they have the ability to call any other NFR config scripts for the same fund/config and student.
